<plot>With seductive words, Robert approaches a woman in a restaurant. After dancing a little, he invites her to his apartment. Meanwhile, at home, Stephanie (age 4), ready to sleep and in bed, asks Mary about her father. At that moment, Robert arrives kissing the woman he found in the restaurant. Stephanie hears the noise and leaves her bedroom running, followed by Mary. An unexpected encounter occurs.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?282180</url></doc>
